The program demonstrates some basic stack operations.

Possible Operations that can be carried out:

	1.Push	  : Push an element into the stack.
	2.Pop 	  : Pop the top of the stack.
	3.Peek	  : Get the top of the stack.
	4.Display : Display the contents of the stack.
	5.Inspect : Check if the expression contained in the stack is valid or not.
		    [ Basically matches opening and closing brackets ]
	6.Postfix : Converts the "VALID" infix expression contained in the stack to postfix.
